CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FIran, Israel and the US lashed out at
OL,7,Feach other over Tuesday night as
OL,8,FTehran sought vengeance for the
OL,9,Fkilling of one of its top leaders.
OL,11,FThe US said it had struck Iranian
OL,12,Fmissile sites along the Straits of
OL,13,FHormuz with large bombs capable of
OL,14,Fpenetrating bunkers.
OL,16,FIn a post on X, the US Central Command
OL,17,Fsaid US forces had "successfully
OL,18,Femployed multiple 5,000-pound deep
OL,19,Fpenetrator munitions on hardened
OL,20,FIranian missile sites."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FThe strikes were aimed at reducing
OL,7,FIran's ability to keep the Straits of
OL,8,FHormuz closed, something that has
OL,9,Ffrustrated Donald Trump in recent days.
OL,11,FIn Iran, the Bushehr nuclear power
OL,12,Fplant complex was hit by a projectile,
OL,13,Fbut there were no injuries, and the
OL,14,Fplant suffered no damage, the
OL,15,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency
OL,16,Fsaid after receiving a report from
OL,17,FTehran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FThe price of Brent crude oil remained
OL,7,Fstubbornly over $100 per barrel in
OL,8,Fearly trading on Wednesday, up more
OL,9,Fthan 40% from the start of the war.
OL,11,FSince the United States and Israel
OL,12,Fattacked Iran, sparking the war,
OL,13,FTehran has been targeting the energy
OL,14,Finfrastructure of its Gulf Arab
OL,15,Fneighbours, as well as military bases,
OL,16,Fas part of a strategy to drive up oil
OL,17,Fprices and put pressure on Washington
OL,18,Fto back down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FIran claims it has only been targeting
OL,7,Fships connected to the US or Israel,
OL,8,Fwith over 90 ships including oil
OL,9,Ftankers being allowed through.
OL,11,FThe country has been effectively
OL,12,Fexporting oil and profiting from the
OL,13,Fincrease in oil prices, much of it
OL,14,Fgoing to China.
OL,16,FTehran responds to killing of top
OL,17,Fcommander
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
