PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FResponding to the killing of Ali
OL,7,FLarijani, secretary of Iran's Supreme
OL,8,FNational Security Council and one of
OL,9,Fthe country's most powerful figures,
OL,10,Fthe Republican Guard said on Wednesday
OL,11,Fit had targeted central Israel with
OL,12,Fmultiple-warhead missiles, which have
OL,13,Fan increased chance of evading missile
OL,14,Fdefence systems and can overwhelm
OL,15,Fradar tracking systems.
OL,17,FIsrael reported at least two salvoes
OL,18,Fof incoming fire and the country's
OL,19,Fmedical service said two people were
OL,20,Fkilled in Ramat Gan, east of Tel Aviv.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
