PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,7,FGuard said the force launched the
OL,8,FKhorramshahr-4 and Qadr multiple-
OL,9,Fwarhead missiles to avenge Larijani's
OL,10,Fkilling.
OL,12,FLarijani, a former parliamentary
OL,13,Fspeaker, was a senior policy adviser
OL,14,Fto the late Supreme Leader Ali
OL,15,FKhamenei on strategy in nuclear talks
OL,16,Fwith the Trump administration.
OL,18,FHe was also believed to be behind the
OL,19,Fsuppression of protests inside Iran.
OL,21,FIsrael continues attacks on Lebanon
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
