PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FIsrael flattened an apartment building
OL,7,Fin central Beirut about an hour after
OL,8,Fissuing an evacuation notice.
OL,10,FIt was the fourth time the building
OL,11,Fhas been targeted, but three strikes
OL,12,Flast week failed to bring it down.
OL,14,FIsrael's military claimed the building
OL,15,Fwas being used by Hezbollah to store
OL,16,F"millions of dollars intended to
OL,17,Ffinance its activities," without
OL,18,Fproviding evidence.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FThere were no immediate reports of
OL,7,Fcasualties, but other attacks on
OL,8,Fapartment buildings in central Beirut
OL,9,Fhave killed at least six people and
OL,10,Fwounded 24 others, according to
OL,11,FLebanon's Health Ministry.
OL,13,FThe Israeli military also said it had
OL,14,Fbegun a wave of strikes targeting
OL,15,FHezbollah in southern Lebanon "in
OL,16,Fresponse to firing into Israeli
OL,17,Fterritory".
OL,26,@wD@_OUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
