FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773843068
OL,3,CUS targets Iranian missile sites near
OL,4,CStrait of Hormuz with powerful bombs
OL,6,FIsrael's strikes have displaced more
OL,7,Fthan 1 million Lebanese ` roughly 20%
OL,8,Fof the population ` according to the
OL,9,FLebanese government, which says more
OL,10,Fthan 900 people have been killed.
OL,12,FIn Israel, 14 people have been killed
OL,13,Fby Iranian missile fire. At least 13
OL,14,FUS military members have been killed.
OL,16,FMore than 1,300 people have been
OL,17,Fkilled in Iran since the conflict
OL,18,Fstarted, according to the Iranian Red
OL,19,FCrescent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
